Pre-Stage-7 readiness rules for Agency OS.

Rules:
- Work in one pass per session.
- Do not jump to Stage 7 until all pre-Stage-7 passes are complete.
- Do not add new product features.
- Do not redesign architecture.
- Preserve working flows.
- Prefer low-risk hardening, consistency, and QA over feature expansion.
- Stop after the active pass and provide a completion report.

Pre-Stage-7 passes:
1. UI Completeness Pass
2. RBAC QA Pass
3. Payments / Compensation Sanity Pass
4. Dashboard Payment Snapshot Pass

General constraints:
- No unrelated UI redesign.
- No mobile work.
- No notification system.
- No approval workflow expansion.
- No analytics expansion outside the scoped dashboard payment snapshot pass.
